{
  "total_duration": 694.833,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 9.896,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Success story"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“成功者的故事”。但先别把它听成一篇“努力就会变有钱”的演讲。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 10.246,
      "end": 23.35,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课真正好玩的地方，是一个人生闭环："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Frank Hawkins"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "从修自行车起步，后来做到一家大公司的负责人，最后家里还是请他去修一辆自行车。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 23.699,
      "end": 45.859,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以记忆线不是“发财了”，而是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "small shop"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "repair bicycles"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "fourteen hours"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "saved money"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "own workshop"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "spare parts"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "two helpers"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "large factory"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "grandson's bicycle"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 46.209,
      "end": 63.524,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先解释几个背景词。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "retired"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是退休，不再全职工作；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "small shop"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里像一个小修理铺；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "workshop"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是小作坊，小工作间；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "factory"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是更大的工厂。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 63.874,
      "end": 75.362,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "还有一个容易误会的语法："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "used to"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。它不是“用某个东西去做什么”，而是“过去经常这样，或者过去是这样，现在不是平常状态了”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 75.711,
      "end": 85.191,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后的自行车请求不是嘲笑 Frank。它很温暖：一个人走了很长的成功之路，但最早学会的本事，仍然能在家里派上用场。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 85.541,
      "end": 99.573,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "故事从回忆开始："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Yesterday afternoon Frank Hawkins was telling me about his experiences as a young man."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "experiences"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是经历，是一个人经历过、记得住的事情。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 99.923,
      "end": 112.411,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Before he retired, Frank was the head of a very large business company."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the head of"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是负责人、领导者；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "business company"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是商业公司。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 112.76,
      "end": 124.096,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但是过去的 Frank 不是一开始就站在大公司里。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "As a boy he used to work in a small shop."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "小时候，他曾经在一家小店里工作。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 124.446,
      "end": 135.734,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他的工作很实际："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It was his job to repair bicycles"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "repair"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是修理，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "bicycle"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是 bike，自行车。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 136.084,
      "end": 149.131,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那时他很辛苦："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "At that time he used to work fourteen hours a day."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "注意这里两个"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "used to"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，都在讲过去的习惯和过去的生活状态。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 149.481,
      "end": 158.905,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "接着是第一步成长："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He saved money for years."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "save money"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是攒钱、存钱，不是“救钱”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 159.255,
      "end": 170.903,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "In 1958 he bought a small workshop of his own."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "of his own"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是属于他自己的。以前他在别人的小店做工，现在他有了自己的小作坊。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 171.253,
      "end": 180.933,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里要看出画面变化：不是一夜暴富，而是 long practice, long hours, saved money, then a workshop of his own。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 181.282,
      "end": 192.022,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "workshop"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "比"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "factory"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "小得多，可以是修理、制作、加工的小地方。Frank 的路是从小地方开始的。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 192.372,
      "end": 202.184,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "再往上走一层："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "In his twenties Frank used to make spare parts for aeroplanes."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "in his twenties"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是二十多岁的时候。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 202.534,
      "end": 213.35,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "spare parts for aeroplanes"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不需要讲成航空课。它就是给飞机使用的机器零件，可能用来维修，也可能用来制造。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 213.699,
      "end": 220.875,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那时规模还小："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "At that time he had two helpers."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "两个帮手，不是一大群员工。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 221.225,
      "end": 234.017,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但几年后变化完成了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "In a few years the small workshop had become a large factory."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had become"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "表示到后来回头看时，小作坊已经变成大工厂了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 234.367,
      "end": 248.759,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这个数字很关键："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The factory employed seven hundred and twenty-eight people."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "employed"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是雇用。two helpers 和 seven hundred and twenty-eight people 一对比，scale 就出来了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 249.108,
      "end": 255.78,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "到这里，Frank 的确有了"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a long road to success"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，一条很长的成功之路。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 256.13,
      "end": 268.366,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Frank smiled when he remembered his hard early years and the long road to success."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他想起早年的艰难，也想起一路走来的成长，所以笑了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 268.716,
      "end": 275.452,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后故事突然回到生活里："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He was still smiling when the door opened and his wife came in."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 275.802,
      "end": 287.761,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后一击很轻，也很暖："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She wanted him to repair their grandson's bicycle!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "孙子的自行车需要修，所以家人又想起了 Frank 最早的本事。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 288.111,
      "end": 296.871,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这就是标题里的 human success story：成功没有抹掉起点，反而让起点变成一个家里人都会记得的技能。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 297.221,
      "end": 299.741,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课为什么不能讲成普通成功学？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 300.091,
      "end": 303.853,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为它不是只说 Frank worked hard and became rich？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 304.203,
      "end": 316.923,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。hard work 很重要，但这课的 punchline 是 bicycle loop。开头他"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "used to repair bicycles"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，结尾妻子让他"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "repair their grandson's bicycle"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 317.273,
      "end": 319.686,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那妻子是在笑他吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 320.035,
      "end": 331.035,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是。她不是 mocking him。这个结尾很 family, very warm。Frank 可能管理过很大的公司，但在家里，他还是那个会修自行车的人。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 331.385,
      "end": 335.138,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "used to"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是不是“用来做”的意思？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 335.488,
      "end": 348.456,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课里不是。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He used to work in a small shop"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“他过去常在小店工作，现在不是这样”。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He used to make spare parts"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“他二十多岁时曾经做这件事”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 348.806,
      "end": 354.98,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "workshop"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "factory"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "怎么分？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 355.33,
      "end": 371.59,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "workshop"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是小作坊、小工作间；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "factory"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是更大的生产场所，可以 employ many workers。Frank 从 two helpers 走到 seven hundred and twenty-eight people，这个对比就是成长。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 371.94,
      "end": 380.86,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天背诵时，就把它当成 ladder with a loop：从 bicycle 起步，爬到 factory，最后又回到 grandson's bicycle。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 381.21,
      "end": 386.658,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Yesterday afternoon Frank Hawkins was telling me about his experiences as a young man."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 387.008,
      "end": 393.944,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Before he retired, Frank was the head of a very large business company, but as a boy he used to work in a small shop."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 394.294,
      "end": 399.694,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It was his job to repair bicycles and at that time he used to work fourteen hours a day."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 400.043,
      "end": 405.323,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
